   5:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   * @brief   RTC HAL module driver.
   6:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *          This file provides firmware functions to manage the following
   7:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *          functionalities of the Real-Time Clock (RTC) peripheral:
   8:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + Initialization/de-initialization functions
   9:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + Calendar (Time and Date) configuration
