  12:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + TimeStamp configuration
  13:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + Tampers configuration
  14:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + Backup Data Registers configuration
  15:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + RTC Tamper and TimeStamp Pins Selection
  16:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc.c ****   *           + Interrupts and flags management
